    "body": "Hi @sherodtaylor! We are sorry for the late reply :(\r\n\r\nI just saw that the standard implies that the royalty is voluntary. If this is the case, then the best way for it would be to create a batch of two transactions: the one which swaps the nfts for some other token and the one which actually pays the royalty. More details can be found here: https://zksync.io/api/sdk/js/accounts.html#batch-builder ",
